30#if !defined(ATF_C_FS_H)
31#define ATF_C_FS_H
32
33#include <sys/types.h>
34#include <sys/stat.h>
35
36#include <stdarg.h>
37#include <stdbool.h>
38
39#include <atf-c/defs.h>
40#include <atf-c/error_fwd.h>
41
42#include "dynstr.h"
43
44/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
45 * The "atf_fs_path" type.
46 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
47
48struct atf_fs_path {
49 atf_dynstr_t m_data;
50};
51typedef struct atf_fs_path atf_fs_path_t;
52
53/* Constructors/destructors. */
54atf_error_t atf_fs_path_init_ap(atf_fs_path_t *, const char *, va_list)
55 ATF_DEFS_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 0);
56atf_error_t atf_fs_path_init_fmt(atf_fs_path_t *, const char *, ...)
57 ATF_DEFS_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 3);
58atf_error_t atf_fs_path_copy(atf_fs_path_t *, const atf_fs_path_t *);
59void atf_fs_path_fini(atf_fs_path_t *);
60
61/* Getters. */
62atf_error_t atf_fs_path_branch_path(const atf_fs_path_t *, atf_fs_path_t *);
63const char *atf_fs_path_cstring(const atf_fs_path_t *);
64atf_error_t atf_fs_path_leaf_name(const atf_fs_path_t *, atf_dynstr_t *);
65bool atf_fs_path_is_absolute(const atf_fs_path_t *);
66bool atf_fs_path_is_root(const atf_fs_path_t *);
67
68/* Modifiers. */
69atf_error_t atf_fs_path_append_ap(atf_fs_path_t *, const char *, va_list)
70 ATF_DEFS_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 0);
71atf_error_t atf_fs_path_append_fmt(atf_fs_path_t *, const char *, ...)
72 ATF_DEFS_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 3);
73atf_error_t atf_fs_path_append_path(atf_fs_path_t *, const atf_fs_path_t *);
74atf_error_t atf_fs_path_to_absolute(const atf_fs_path_t *, atf_fs_path_t *);
75
76/* Operators. */
77bool atf_equal_fs_path_fs_path(const atf_fs_path_t *,
78 const atf_fs_path_t *);
79
80/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
81 * The "atf_fs_stat" type.
82 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
83
84struct atf_fs_stat {
85 int m_type;
86 struct stat m_sb;
87};
88typedef struct atf_fs_stat atf_fs_stat_t;
89
90/* Constants. */
91extern const int atf_fs_stat_blk_type;
92extern const int atf_fs_stat_chr_type;
93extern const int atf_fs_stat_dir_type;
94extern const int atf_fs_stat_fifo_type;
95extern const int atf_fs_stat_lnk_type;
96extern const int atf_fs_stat_reg_type;
97extern const int atf_fs_stat_sock_type;
98extern const int atf_fs_stat_wht_type;
99
100/* Constructors/destructors. */
101atf_error_t atf_fs_stat_init(atf_fs_stat_t *, const atf_fs_path_t *);
102void atf_fs_stat_copy(atf_fs_stat_t *, const atf_fs_stat_t *);
103void atf_fs_stat_fini(atf_fs_stat_t *);
104
105/* Getters. */
106dev_t atf_fs_stat_get_device(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
107ino_t atf_fs_stat_get_inode(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
108mode_t atf_fs_stat_get_mode(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
109off_t atf_fs_stat_get_size(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
110int atf_fs_stat_get_type(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
111bool atf_fs_stat_is_owner_readable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
112bool atf_fs_stat_is_owner_writable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
113bool atf_fs_stat_is_owner_executable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
114bool atf_fs_stat_is_group_readable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
115bool atf_fs_stat_is_group_writable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
116bool atf_fs_stat_is_group_executable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
117bool atf_fs_stat_is_other_readable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
118bool atf_fs_stat_is_other_writable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
119bool atf_fs_stat_is_other_executable(const atf_fs_stat_t *);
120
121/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
122 * Free functions.
123 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
124
125extern const int atf_fs_access_f;
126extern const int atf_fs_access_r;
127extern const int atf_fs_access_w;
128extern const int atf_fs_access_x;
129
130atf_error_t atf_fs_eaccess(const atf_fs_path_t *, int);
131atf_error_t atf_fs_exists(const atf_fs_path_t *, bool *);
132atf_error_t atf_fs_getcwd(atf_fs_path_t *);
133atf_error_t atf_fs_mkdtemp(atf_fs_path_t *);
134atf_error_t atf_fs_mkstemp(atf_fs_path_t *, int *);
135atf_error_t atf_fs_rmdir(const atf_fs_path_t *);
136atf_error_t atf_fs_unlink(const atf_fs_path_t *);
137
138#endif /* !defined(ATF_C_FS_H) */
